{"word":"καταβρίθω","slug":"καταβρίθω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταβρίθω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-βρίσω</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-βέβρῑθα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be heavily laden</i> or <i>weighed down by</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to weigh down, to outweigh</i>, <el>ὄλβῳ κ. βασιλῆας</el> <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}